  "text": "I cannot believe my eyes! We are here for the World Cup on 26 June 2026, and Norway have just been absolutely dismantled by France! I am shaking, I am absolutely livid, how can this be the result?!\n\nFrance came out like a freight train in the opening moment to strike a shot and make it 0-1. How do we respond? We don't! Moments later, Norway are already picking up yellow cards as the pressure mounts, and then, soon after, France strike again with another shot to extend the lead to 0-2. It is a disaster! A total catastrophe!\n\nBut listen, we weren't finished! Moments later, we fought back! Norway found a way! We pulled one back with a shot to make it 1-2! For a second, there was hope, a glimmer of light in this darkness! But France are just too clinical, too ruthless! Soon after, they struck a shot to make it 1-3 and we were heading into the break trailing by two goals.\n\nThe second half was a mountain we just couldn't climb. We had some corners, yes, we earned four corners in total, but France were clinical. A yellow card was shown to France much later, but it didn't stop the bleeding. A while later, the nightmare was completed; France rose for a header to make it 1-4. \n\nI am speechless! How did we let them dictate the tempo like that? We fought, we struggled, but the scoreboard tells the cold, hard truth. The final score was 1-4! My heart is broken! Norway deserved better, but France were simply too strong today! What a devastating result to witness!",
